{"word":"Sobriety","slug":"sobriety","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Sobriety</b> Commanded<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=1&verse=13'>1Pe 1:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=5&verse=8'>1Pe 5:8</a><br/> The gospel designed to teach<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=56&chapter=2&verse=12'>Tit 2:12</a><br/> With watchfulness<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=52&chapter=5&verse=6'>1Th 5:6</a><br/> With prayer<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=4&verse=7'>1Pe 4:7</a><br/> Required in:<br/> - Ministers<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=3&verse=3'>1Ti 3:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=56&chapter=1&verse=8'>Tit 1:8</a> <br/> - Wives of ministers<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=3&verse=11'>1Ti 3:11</a> <br/> - Aged men<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=56&chapter=2&verse=2'>Tit 2:2</a> <br/> - Young men<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=56&chapter=2&verse=6'>Tit 2:6</a> <br/> - Young women<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=56&chapter=2&verse=4'>Tit 2:4</a> <br/> - All saints<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=52&chapter=5&verse=6'>1Th 5:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=52&chapter=5&verse=8'>1Th 5:8</a> <br/> Women should exhibit in dress<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=2&verse=9'>1Ti 2:9</a><br/> We should estimate our character and talents with<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=12&verse=3'>Rom 12:3</a><br/> We should live in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=56&chapter=2&verse=12'>Tit 2:12</a><br/> Motive for<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=4&verse=7'>1Pe 4:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=5&verse=8'>1Pe 5:8</a><br/><a href='S:Temperance'>Temperance</a>; <a href='S:Drunkenness'>Drunkenness</a>"}]}